you use if statments to get mutiple choice options. so for example you would use a if statment for tempeture.
if the tempture is above freezing you wear a jacket. else if the temp is bellow freezing you wear a coat.
else you wear your normal cloths. so if the temp is above freezing your good, else if the temp is bellow freezing you wear a coat, else you dont wear a coat or jacket.
